{
  "id": "69c65d5cb2a906f7ec759f11",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:朝ルーティン",
  "created": 1774607739,
  "updated": 1774607753,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c65d5cb2a906f7ec759f11",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:朝ルーティン",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607739,
      "updated": 1774607739
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7a0000000000485791",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607739,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c0000000000485792",
      "text": "「はーいみんな〜、今日のテーマは『[朝ルーティン]』だよ〜！朝ってさ、ガチで人生の勝敗分かれる時間じゃね？って思うんだけどw みんなどんな感じ〜？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c0000000000485793",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c0000000000485794",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c0000000000485795",
      "text": "「朝というのは、一日のはじまりをそっと告げる大切な時間でございますね。静かな光が差し込む中で過ごすひとときは、心を整える儀式のようでもありますわ（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c0000000000485796",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c0000000000485797",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c0000000000485798",
      "text": "「概念的には同意。朝の行動は、その日の認知パフォーマンスや意思決定に影響する。いわば“初期条件の設定”だね。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c0000000000485799",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c000000000048579a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c000000000048579b",
      "text": "「でたでた、りかの“それっぽい用語”w 要するに“朝ミスると1日バグる”ってことっしょ？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c000000000048579c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c000000000048579d",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c000000000048579e",
      "text": "「…意訳としては正しい。簡潔で良い。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c000000000048579f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857a0",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857a1",
      "text": "「まあ、“バグる”という表現は少々荒々しい気もいたしますが、言い得て妙かもしれませんね（笑う）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857a2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857a3",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857a4",
      "text": "「でさでさ、あや姉は絶対ちゃんとしてる系でしょ？優雅に紅茶とか飲んでそう」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857a5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857a6",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857a7",
      "text": "「いえ、そこまで優雅ではございませんよ。ただ、起きたらまず窓を開けて空気を入れ替え、それから白湯を少し……体を内側から目覚めさせるようにしております」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857a8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857a9",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857aa",
      "text": "「うわ、意識高っ…！白湯とかガチ勢じゃん…！うちはアラーム5回スヌーズしてからスマホ直行だわw」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857ab",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857ac",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857ad",
      "text": "「典型的なドーパミン先行型行動だね。起床直後のSNSは注意力を分散させやすいという研究もある」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857ae",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857af",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857b0",
      "text": "「え、なにそれ怖…“朝イチSNSは地雷”ってこと？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857b1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857b2",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857b3",
      "text": "「簡略化すればそう。起床後すぐの刺激は、その後の集中力に影響する」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857b4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857b5",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857b6",
      "text": "「朝の静けさを大切にする、という考えにも通じますね。慌ただしい情報の波に飲み込まれる前に、自分自身と向き合う時間を持つ……なんて、少し詩的すぎるでしょうか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857b7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857b8",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857b9",
      "text": "「いや、なんかエモい…！でもさ〜現実問題ムリじゃね？朝って戦争じゃん？時間ないしw」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857ba",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857bb",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857bc",
      "text": "「だからこそルーティン化する。意思決定のコストを削減するために、行動を固定化するのが有効。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857bd",
      "text": "例えば――",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857be",
      "text": " 起床",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857bf",
      "text": " 水分補給",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857c0",
      "text": " 軽いストレッチ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857c1",
      "text": " 朝食",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857c2",
      "text": "この順序を“テンプレ化”する」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857c3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857c4",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857c5",
      "text": "「テンプレ朝活w それコピペで生きてる感じしてちょい草」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857c6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857c7",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857c8",
      "text": "「けれど、決まりごとがあるからこそ、心に余白が生まれることもありますわ。日々の繰り返しの中に、小さな安らぎを見出す……そんな朝も素敵ではありませんか（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857c9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857ca",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857cb",
      "text": "「なんか今日のあや姉、文学バフかかってるな…」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857cc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857cd",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857ce",
      "text": "「要点をまとめるね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857cf",
      "text": " 朝は一日のパフォーマンスを左右する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857d0",
      "text": " スマホ即使用は注意力低下のリスク",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857d1",
      "text": " ルーティン化で意思決定コスト削減",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857d2",
      "text": " 精神的な余白も重要",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857d3",
      "text": "――以上。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857d4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857d5",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857d6",
      "text": "「急に会議のまとめみたいになったw」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857d7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857d8",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857d9",
      "text": "「とても分かりやすいですわ。りかさんのその整理の仕方、いつも助かっております」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857da",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857db",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857dc",
      "text": "「どういたしまして。…ただし、私の朝は理想通りではない。実際は二度寝との戦闘から始まる」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857dd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857de",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857df",
      "text": "「え、りかも人間だったんだw」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857e0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857e1",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857e2",
      "text": "「どなたにも、少しの“ゆらぎ”はあるものですわね（笑う）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774607740,
      "updated": 1774607740
    },
    {
      "id": "69c65d7c00000000004857e3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
